│ (`malloc(): corrupted top size`) and the subsequent `SIGABRT`.                             │
│                                                                                            │
│ The fundamental flaw is that `getEntryCost` does not properly handle the failure from      │
│ `canSchedule` and continues execution with an invalid `Schedule` state.                    │
│                                                                                            │
